11#include "ipf.h"
12
13
14wordtab_t *findword(words, name)
15 wordtab_t *words;
16 char *name;
17{
18 wordtab_t *w;
19
20 for (w = words; w->w_word != NULL; w++)
21 if (!strcmp(name, w->w_word))
22 break;
23 if (w->w_word == NULL)
24 return NULL;
25
26 return w;
27}
